      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still super dependable and ready for many more adventures. It drives like a dream and has been kept up nicely. If you're looking for a great, reliable vehicle that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
