    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a precision-engineered mid-engine specimen, powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus for a linear power band and immediate throttle response. Mated to a 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain offers short-throw engagement and a visceral connection to the pavement. The chassis is anchored by a MacPherson strut suspension and enhanced by four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers, ensuring exceptional deceleration and cornering poise. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, including recent cooling system service and a comprehensive inspection of the bores. While displaying minor aesthetic patina from spirited use, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the structural integrity is uncompromising. An ideal acquisition for the driver who prioritizes analog feedback and balanced weight distribution.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
